The '''Multrong''', who was also referred to as the '''Eastlord''', was the title given to the ruler of [[Mulptan]] in [[Rashemen]].
document_data.History: The title of Multrong was granted by Rahsemen's [[Iron Lord]]. The Multrong's decisions heavily influenced Multpan's trade and commerce.
